leid=\"506240178\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.4141630901287554\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"466\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=497bce68&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9dqiapibYyenia2QFqCZSLN5tQpiazt4JicjRiajbDWsUPPomjibCY6oaic9Rqr6kqrInzBN7ylYLjBVJINQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">来看看这个APP长啥样吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以看到，M2.1对APP整体的设计理解和美学表达，都还挺靠谱的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">再来看一个安卓端的手机游戏（by官方）。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" data-website=\"https://www.mdnice.com\" style=\"background-size:auto;background-attachment:scroll;padding-left:10px;font-size:16px;overflow-wrap:break-word;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);background-repeat:no-repeat;word-spacing:0em;background-position-x:0%;background-position-y:0%;word-break:break-word;margin-top:0px;font-family:Optima, 'Microsoft YaHei', PingFangSC-regular, serif;background-image:none;text-align:left;padding-top:0px;letter-spacing:0em;padding-bottom:0px;line-height:1.5em;margin-right:0px;background-clip:border-box;width:auto;background-origin:padding-box;margin-bottom:0px;padding-right:10px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n  <pre data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55) 0px 2px 10px;text-align: left;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;margin-left: 4px;margin-right: 4px;padding-top: 0px;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-right: 0px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:5px;padding:16px;padding-top:15px;display:-webkit-box;overflow-x:auto;font-size:12px;font-family:Consolas, Monaco, Menlo, monospace;\"><span leaf=\"\">用Kotlin语言开发一款重力感应模拟器，利用陀螺仪传感器实现重力操控体验，并设计有巧妙的视觉彩蛋。</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 16px 8px 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以看到，UI的过渡和碰撞特效非常自然，而且巧妙的呈现了“MERRY XMAS MiniMax M2.1”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前，很多coding模型都在拼命表现自己web端很强，但移动端的开发能力就只字不提。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其实，移动端才是研发的大头。很高兴，今天见到有模型开始在Android、iOS开发上发力了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而且，M2.1是具备APP开发从0到1再到100的能力的（比如我前面那个case）。这一点，真的牛逼。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: underline;\">4）后端开发</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">过去，很多模型在宣发时，都强调自己前端很强、UI很酷。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但这能代表coding能力吗？未必。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">前端很重要，但它不是全部。唯有前后端一起进化，才能做出真正生产级的产品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">M2.1这次着重在后端上做了提升，从Java后端到Golang服务，到C++，到客户端、SDK……各个开发环节都有所加强。不再聚焦前端demo，而是关注整个开发环节。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是第一次有coding模型，开始理解不同的技术岗位是怎么写代码的，去帮助各种开发环节解决编码问题。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">给大家看几个例子。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">帮我写一个跨平台C++文件读写工具。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjimy51m1n16\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506240171\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.677304964539007\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"846\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4e7206ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9dqiapibYyenia2QFqCZSLN5txl9K2qONkwvDn0AcvN5sWokma5ZVq8O1Q2tD0COEmXEqRuickZMMmFA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">让它写一个用户鉴权模块，一看就是Java老手。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjitp9id3cx\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506240179\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0610412926391382\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"557\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=761c57fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9dqiapibYyenia2QFqCZSLN5tJokYWxlfD4v676gmYl1UCQcXj1fQ56Nt5F5JWbWb3k8yb53cLA5lcQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">用C++和GLSL渲染图像，精准还原水晶球的物理折射、雪人建模以及雪地特效。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我的体验感觉是，M2.1让AI Coding开始从“单文件”向“工程感”进发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它的后端能力肯定不是最强的，也还有很多需要优化的地方。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但我们终于在M2.1上看到，Coding模型开始从“前端友好”向“后端友好”进化，而不再是让demo写法当成生产代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">终于，有一个正常的coding模型把大家拉回正轨，开始解决真实世界中的复杂任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506236478\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.22833333333333333\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54b71409&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FNX4HOlP6ibCicV1QppcudDqHNibe1FiaSiaXvaAstRwhiayia3Y48FgMzdQ7LPRGS3mz0iaKmBic96xZwHoc195LUjDPUow%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(210, 79, 240);font-weight: bold;\">怎么使用</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">API</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">MiniMax开放平台已经上线，模型名MiniMax-M2.1，支持OpenAI&amp;Anthropic接口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://platform.minimaxi.com/docs/guides/text-generation\" target=\"_blank\">https://platform.minimaxi.com/docs/guides/text-generation</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">Coding Plan</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">同时，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">M2.1已加入Coding Plan，加量不加价。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.6em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\"><a href=\"https://platform.minimaxi.com/subscribe/coding-plan\" target=\"_blank\">https://platform.minimaxi.com/subscribe/coding-plan</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;padding: 0.5em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjiudwhk1pt4\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"506240180\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.43231441048034935\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"916\" style=\"box-shadow: rgb(210, 210, 210) 0px 0px 0.5em 0px;background-color: transparent;border-radius: 6px;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=66c5e3dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FNX4HOlP6ibC9dqiapibYyenia2QFqCZSLN5tDEXDF6AAlB2AS4g